{"tid":2492584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【2021年】【0417 LIVE】衞生署及醫管局4點半疫情簡報會","createTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T08:26:44.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cef1531ab3ad9e8859dbb933a4c3eed176280e3f","tid":2492584,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>是日出席代表：衞生防護中心總監林文健、衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君、醫院管理局總行政經理（質素及標準）劉家獻</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e89dcc1e99b4a785c9d6b68b511440f4ed87e7","tid":2492584,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NwQ_AqdKG8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNwQ_AqdKG8g&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=09d113c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NwQ_AqdKG8g</a>"},{"pid":"1456a787da805a6f6b95d8ae372a1c1f702470bb","tid":2492584,"uid":244704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NwQ_AqdKG8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNwQ_AqdKG8g&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=09d113c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NwQ_AqdKG8g</a>"},{"pid":"234118ba584ce7bf6a94315b55fa6d264b6f331d","tid":2492584,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"長壽節目 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793197e3374a3c310a8346eaf2d9a343f26fdc36","tid":2492584,"uid":260251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"05ab35f67a08cb77432da9b6c47eef94961581be","tid":2492584,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:11.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"b5a4931a7b12318ee155f6d8c15b11f21dd8663d","tid":2492584,"uid":246731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e179d4de53283770801abf02ae4404c4d00d461","tid":2492584,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>599J強制檢測途徑：</strong><br />\n（一）於流動採樣站接受檢測服務（名單及服務對象：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=5f0748f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[中資]<br />\n（二）於社區檢測中心接受檢測服務（名單：<a href=\"http://www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=586b5804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/</a>）[中資]<br />\n（三）於121間郵政局、20個港鐵站設置的自動派發機或醫院管理局47間指定普通科門診診所索取深喉唾液測試樣本收集包，並把樣本交回指定樣本收集點（派發點及時間，以及樣本收集點及時間：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=5f0748f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[中資]<br />\n（四）於醫管局普通科門診診所按照醫管局醫護人員的指示接受檢測<br />\n（五）自行安排接受由衞生署認可，並可就檢測結果發出電話短訊通知的私營化驗所提供的檢測（名單：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FList_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=71ff2e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf</a>）<br />\n（六）使用衞生防護中心派發到相關指明地方的樣本瓶（如適用），並按有關指示交回已採樣本的檢測樣本收集瓶。"},{"pid":"4a91ce9990e6d60f656a145a6de4affed09a978a","tid":2492584,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"好多輸入<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe91b2900a6dbef08fb5b4c5b6088b6a052f4fa","tid":2492584,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05e89dcc1e99b4a785c9d6b68b511440f4ed87e7","tid":2492584,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NwQ_AqdKG8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNwQ_AqdKG8g&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=09d113c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NwQ_AqdKG8g</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2a59503f976374d6fdf31cac21091dfc3f27f7","tid":2492584,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"N501Y<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317fe36e4f926fbbe8500d6cd4b0d7068ac2d642","tid":2492584,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>武肺民間資訊</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=654deb54\" data-auto-link target=\"_b